* BMAP phase-5 EDEC test (decimal-edit literals -> .obj byte-walk).
* Each EDEC field is <count><A|P>[L]<number>: A=9-bit ASCII, P=4-bit packed.
*   4A123  -> one 9-bit word, leading-zero filled to width 4.
*   5P+12  -> one 4-bit packed word, '+' overpunch (014), 2 leading zeros.
*   6A1.5  -> floating: '+' sign byte, fill, digits, trailing scale byte (two
*             words); DP=-1 -> scale 0377.
       OUNAME EDECTST
       EDEC   4A123
       EDEC   5P+12
       EDEC   6A1.5
       END
